     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <head>To the Reader.</head>
   <l>SOme men there be that praise whats good they heare</l>
   <l>And some there are that carpe what ere it be:</l>
   <l>Some men in <hi>Zoilus</hi> ghost will soone appeare,</l>
   <l>And some with <hi>Aristippus</hi> flattery,</l>
   <l>But carpe at what you can, dispraise, back-bite,</l>
   <l>Ile neuer hide my Poems from the light.</l>
</div>
